    <string name="about_text">NoteWorld is about making your world easier, you can save your thoughts, ideas, things to do and anything here. You can set up a lock screen to keep things private. Here are the services this app provides: \n\n
                                1. Save and Edit your notes\n
                                2. Share/send you notes to email or drive or any other app\n
                                3. Lock screen to protect your data\n
                                4. Delete your notes from the list\n
                                5. Search notes from the list\n
                                6. Settings to manage your app\n
                                7. You have options to change the look of your app\n\n
        NoteWorld saves your data only on your device, once you uninstall your app all the data will be deleted. Make sure your you save your data(long press on each note) before uninstalling the app.\n\nWe will try to get more new features to you.</string>

